 Taking to Instagram, Liz Hurley, 57, looked ageless as she posed in the sunshine for some promotional snaps. Advertising her latest addition to her beachwear line, the actress posed on a small cliff overlooking a dazzlingly appealing ocean. Clad in a tiny white bikini, Liz confidently posed for the camera in view her 2.5 million followers on Instagram. Within hours the post had tens of thousands of likes and hundreds of comments. Countless fans fawned over Liz’s looks, with one even lamenting: “(Wish) I was rich or famous enough to have a shot!” Others labelled the model a “dreamwife”, “goddess” and the “essence of human beauty”. 